By: Ibn al-Fârid
Format: verse
---
Yield not to weaknesses that let the hour
Of duty pass. Though thou art palsied, walk,
And rise, though thou be broken; for thy lot
Is worthlessness, if thou defer resolve
Unto the day of health.
